tical challenges and potential safety hazards, according to WSJ. The 890-pound kiosks, often hardwired into stores\u0026#39; electrical systems, require specialized removal.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \n\n\u003cb\u003eFurther reading\u003c/b\u003e: \u003ca href=\"https://entertainment.slashdot.org/story/24/08/15/1648227/redbox-app-axed-dashing-peoples-hopes-of-keeping-purchased-content\"\u003eRedbox App Axed, Dashing People\u0026#39;s Hopes of Keeping Purchased Content\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\u003c/article\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003c/section\u003e\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\u003csection\u003e\n\t\t\u003cblockquote cite=\"https://slashdot.org\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eLo!  Men have become the tool of their tools.\n\t\t-- Henry David Thoreau\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003cspan\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n\t\t\u003c/blockquote\u003e\n\t\u003c/section\u003e\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\u003cimg src=\"https://slashdot.org/adbanner.gif?t=20241011\" alt=\"\"/\u003e\n\t\u003cimg src=\"https://slashdot.org/purple.gif?t=20241011\" alt=\"\"/\u003e\n\t\n\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWorking...\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\t    \n\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\u003c/div\u003e",
